# PeopleSoft adapters

- Treat `.reference/PS-Utilities` as behavior oracle only — do not vendor it into the extension package.
- Detect UI model before DOM assumptions: classic frame vs Fluid header vs nav collection iframe.
- Prefer shared helpers in `src/adapters/ps-page.ts` over duplicating selectors in features.
- Search automation must attempt Fluid selectors, not only `ptifrmtgtframe`.
- Never store PeopleSoft credentials.
